2013年4月23日，宣布將推出續集<ref>{{cite news |date= 2013-04-23|last= Fleming Jr |first= Mike |title= Sequels On Tap For ‘The Heat’ And ‘Ride Along’ |url= http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/sequels-on-tap-for-the-heat-and-ride-along/ |newspaper= deadline.com |accessdate= 2014-04-19 }}</ref>。2014年2月18日，由於第一集的成功，因此提姆·史多利將再次擔任導演並延續本集的故事<ref>{{cite news|last=Ford|first=Rebecca|title='Ride Along 2' Moving Forward With Kevin Hart, Ice Cube in Talks to Return|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ride-along-2-moving-forward-681383|accessdate=2014-02-19|newspaper= [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]  |date=2014-02-18}}</ref>。冰塊酷巴和凱文·哈特回歸演出、威爾·帕克再次擔任監製，以及麥特·曼弗雷迪將繼續編劇。續集於2014年7月7日在[[邁阿密|邁阿密]]和亞特蘭大開拍<ref>{{cite news|last=Busch|first=Anita|title=‘Ride Along 2′ Gets Rolling: Tim Story To Direct, Will Packer To Produce With Deals Closing For Kevin Hart and Ice Cube|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/ride-along-2-gets-rolling-story-to-direct-packer-to-produce-with-deals-closing-for-hart-and-cube/|accessdate=2014-02-19|newspaper=deadline.com|date=2014-02-18}}</ref>。美國的上映日確定為2016年1月15日<ref>{{cite news|last=Kroll|first=Justin|title=‘Ride Along 2′ to Bow on Martin Luther King Weekend 2016|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/ride-along-2-to-bow-on-martin-luther-king-weekend-2016-1201132334/|accessdate=2014-03-14|newspaper=variety.com|date=2014-03-13}}</ref>。2016年1月15日美國上映。

